description:
In a scene resembling something out of a Bollywood movie, when a child who had been kidnapped about 14 months ago in Jaipur was found by the police, he refused to leave the kidnapper. As the police attempted to separate them, the innocent child began to cry.

A heart-wrenching video has emerged from a police station in Jaipur, showing an innocent child clinging tightly to his kidnapper and crying loudly, refusing to let go of him. Seeing the child cry, tears began to flow from the suspect‚Äôs eyes as well. However, a police officer forcefully separated the child from the accused and handed him over to his mother, but the child continued to cry

The police on Wednesday solved a kidnapping case of an 11-month-old baby named Prithvi, which took place 14 months ago in the Sanganer Sadar police station area of Jaipur. The police have arrested the accused head constable, who had a reward of Rs 25,000 on his head. The child has been recovered from his custody.

According to reports, the accused was living as a monk in a hut he built in the Khadar area near the Yamuna River on the Parikrama path in Vrindavan. To conceal his identity, he had grown a beard and long hair.

description:
A video has emerged from Uttar Pradesh‚Äôs Agra showing two men in a motorcycle harassing a woman in full public view.
Many on social media have condemned the brazen criminal action. The Agra Police said they have filed a case and arrested the two men.

‚ÄúTaking immediate cognisance of the viral video of stalking and harassing a girl riding a scooty, the anti-Romeo team immediately filed a case and arrested the two accused and recovered the motorcycle,‚Äù the Agra Police said in a post on X.

The two men were seen on a bike on the right, while there were three men on a bike on the left who were known to the woman and trying to help her, the police said. 

The incident happened at night. The woman was seen riding in the middle of the road, while the two men were tailgating her. One of the men who came to help indicated to the woman with a hand gesture to slow down.

The men on the other bike followed her for several kilometres. The woman managed to find a traffic policeman, who stopped the motorcycle and took her out of harm's way

‚ú©Venus

‚ú©Earth:

Thanks to the wonderful atmosphere, food and water, and everything else that makes our home planet liveable, you can get in a good 80 or more years here. Earth is perfect for us.

description:
Pearls, crystals, glitter... these are not part of #AliaBhatt‚Äôs usual beauty repertoire ‚ú® Of her approach to the hair and makeup chair, the actor (and mom of a toddler) says ‚Äúwhatever needs to happen needs to happen fast.‚Äù But, for an Allure cover, exceptions can be made. At our Mumbai shoot, Bhatt collaborated with makeup artist Kuma, hairstylist Ali Pirzadeh, and manicurist Anisha Mulchandani to dream up these dazzling (and, yes, slightly time-intensive) looks. At the link-in bio, go to our full video interview with Bhatt, where she talks about her everyday makeup routine, her all-time favorite products, and more ‚ú®

description:
Sri Singhanath Temple üõïüòçüôèüèª.

This is a glimpse of Singhanath temple located on Gopinathpur village of Badamba side of Cuttack. It was our first time visit here. We went to this place last August 4th, 2024. Due to some reasons, we were unable to have darshan of the god. But here is some glimpse of Singhanath temple from our side. 

Singhanath Temple is dedicated to Shiva who is worshipped by Narasimha, an avatar of Vishnu. The temple has a rekha deula and terraced roof jagamohana of traditional phase of temple style of Kalingan order. The temple is unique for its sculptural embellishment of both the Saivaite and Vaishnava sects. It is located in the Gopinathpur village, Baramba tehsil of Cuttack district, Odisha, India. It can be easily approached by road from Cuttack, Athgarhand Banki by new Mahanadi bridge. ( Details From @wiki )

Location üìç: Sri Singhanath Temple, Gopinathpur, Badamba, Cuttack, Odisha.

description:
FIGURING OUT HAS A NEW HOME NOW. - Finally!! moved to a new studio today ü•∫

When I left my home, my family business and my city to start something of my own in 2021, with zero money, zero experience, and zero connections. There was only one thought. FEAR.

fear of what if I am not able to make money?
fear of what if I fail?
fear of what will people say?
fear of who will help me?
fear of what if this, what if that?

But I told myself, Raj:
FOR ONCE IN YOUR LIFE
WHAT IF YOU ACTUALLY DID EVERYTHING YOU KNEW YOU
SHOULD DO...
HOW GOOD COULD YOUR LIFE
REALLY BECOME?

and look here we are, I can‚Äôt imagine that I get to learn from the world‚Äôs best every day and apply that in my life and then teach those lessons to everyone.

Thank you so much for supporting us since the beginning, I promise this is still day 1 for us, I promise I will make all of you proud on a world level one day. and we will just keep going upwards.

Me and the whole @figuringout.co team is absolutely GRATEFUL TO GOD‚ÄôS PLAN AND GRATEFUL FOR OUR AUDIENCE ‚ù§Ô∏è üôáüèª‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è

description:
As parents, it seems natural to choose products that sound gentle and natural for baby skin care or massage oils. However, it‚Äôs noteworthy that experts advise against using baby skin care products and oils that contain food ingredients like cow or goat milk, oats, coconut, almond, or peanut oil, especially if the baby has eczema.

Current research is investigating whether infants who are exposed to allergens such as nuts, eggs, and milk through skin care products, rather than through food, are more likely to develop food allergies.

The hypothesis is that a baby‚Äôs immune system may be more likely to tolerate common allergens if they are first introduced through the digestive system, rather than through the skin.

A recent international study found of 276 skincare products marketed for children, nearly 40% included one of more common food allergens.

The most common were:

 Almonds (41.7%)

Wheat (22.4%)

Soy (15.4%)

Oats 10.3%)

Sesame (8.3%)

Milk (1.3%

Peanuts (0.6%)

description:
Ibunda Afif Maulana, Anggun Andriani, membeberkan sejumlah luka-luka yang dialami anaknya akibat diduga disiksa polisi. Dugaan ini muncul setelah jasad Afif ditemukan di bawah Jembatan Kuranji, Padang.‚Å†
‚Å†
Salah satu luka yang dinilai janggal oleh Anggun adalah jejak sepatu yang diduga dari oknum aparat. Jejak sepatu itu diketahui saat jasad Afif akan dimandikan.‚Å†
‚Å†
"Ada luka memar di sebelah kiri, terus di perutnya ini ada pukulan dari sepatu oknum. Soalnya Afif itu dimandikan banyak orang di rumah, ada Marinir pun yang mandikan yang dekat sama Afif itu kan, Itu tuh tanda sepatu oknum itu. Sekampung dia orang tinggal Afif itu semuanya," kata Anggun di kawasan Kuningan, Jakarta Selatan, Rabu (3/7).‚Å†
‚Å†
Maka itu, Anggun meyakini anaknya tidak melompat dari sungai seperti yang disampaikan polisi. Apalagi berdasarkan informasi yang didapatnya, Afif dibawa ke Polsek Kuranji dan disiksa oleh polisi.‚Å†
‚Å†
üì∏: Dok. kumparan.‚Å†
‚Å†

description:
Cucumber Sandwiches With Healthy Homemade Cream Cheese Spread

You must try this light, refreshing & delicious cucumber sandwich with creamy, healthy, protein rich, and flavorful homemade cream cheese spreadü§§‚ù§Ô∏è

This quick 5 minute recipe is perfect for lunch on the go, tea time snack, breakfast, party starter, picnic, potluck and moreüòç

Quick, easy, and so tasty! üòã 

üìå Save & Share the recipe!
Follow @thehealthyrasoi for more

Ingredients:- 
For cream cheese spread:-
1/2 cup fresh paneer
1 tbsp fresh curd 
1 big or 2-3 small cloves garlic 
Salt as required 
1/4 tsp black pepper 
2 tsp spring onion, finely chopped 
2 tsp dill/Suva leaves and mix. 

For sandwiches:-
Bread of your choice 
Cucumber slices

Start by blending paneer, curd, and a garlic clove into a creamy paste. Add salt, black pepper, green onion, and fresh dill leaves, then mix well. Thinly slice cucumbers and place them on a paper towel to soak up excess water. Optionally, cut the sides off the bread. Spread the cream cheese mixture on one side of each bread slice, layer cucumber slices on top, and cover with another slice of bread. Cut into your desired shape. To keep them fresh for up to two days, wrap each sandwich in cling film, store in the fridge, and enjoy!

CRUNCHY BOWL WITH SMOKED ONION DRESSING

Sweet Corn - 1/2 cup
Onion - 1

Hung Curd - 1 cup

description:
Seorang dosen Universitas Muhammadiyah Surakarta (UMS), diviralkan oleh mahasiswinya yang merasa dilecehkan secara seksual saat bimbingan skripsi, di rumah dosen tersebut.‚Å†
‚Å†
Berdasarkan cerita korban, dosen tersebut meminta mahasiswi ini memperlihatkan perutnya. Selain itu pelaku mengelus kaki korban (menggunakan kaki), memegang lutut, hingga meminta peluk.‚Å†
‚Å†
Wakil Rektor IV UMS, EM Sutrisna, mengatakan pihaknya masih mengumpulkan bukti terkait peristiwa ini. Ia menyayangkan adanya dugaan pelecehan yang dilakukan oleh dosen pembimbing skripsi terhadap mahasiswinya itu.‚Å†
‚Å†
"Kami sangat prihatin atas kejadian ini. UMS adalah kampus yang menerapkan nilai-nilai Islam Kemuhammadiyahan," kata Sutrisna pada Selasa (9/7).‚Å†
‚Å†

Harshita Kejriwal, the daughter of Delhi Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal, was the victim of an online scam on the e-commerce platform OLX. 
Harshita had listed a used sofa for sale on OLX. A scammer posing as an interested buyer contacted her, gained her trust by sending a small amount to her account, and then asked her to scan a QR code to receive the full payment. However, when Harshita scanned the QR code, the scammer was able to debit Rs 34,000 from her account in two separate transactions of Rs 20,000 and Rs 14,000. 
The scammer used social engineering tactics to exploit Harshita‚Äôs lack of technical knowledge about UPI payments and QR codes. The scammer first sent a small amount to establish credibility, then sent the QR code and asked Harshita to scan it to receive the full payment, but instead the money was debited from her account. 
The Delhi Police have filed a case of cheating and are investigating the incident. Three people have been arrested in connection with the scam, but the main mastermind is still absconding.

description:
Create a Bajrang suraksha kavach (Protective Shield) with Kalava (Moli) and Hanuman Chalisa
.
In this video, we learn how to create a protective shield using Kalava (also called Moli). We are told that by tying 9 knots in the Kalava while reciting the Hanuman Chalisa 9 times, we can protect ourselves, our family members, and even our car from accidents, health problems, negative energy, and the evil eye. The Kalava should be left in the temple overnight and then tied on the right hand for men and the left hand for women to provide this powerful protection.

description:
This is not a post to tell you ‚Äúdon‚Äôt come to Colorado we‚Äôre too full‚Äù‚Ä¶

However, this is a post to challenge you to ask yourself some tough questions the next time you go visit a town that‚Äôs so engraved in nature. 

I‚Äôll start by saying that this specific trail and pass is easily accessed by parking your car in town and taking a FREE bus ride (electric / low emission buses) that spits you out right at the top here. 

Yea you‚Äôll have an extra half a mile to walk, but you will be okay. It‚Äôs part of the experience. ü©∑

Ignorance and laziness have no place in the mountains. 

Take the extra time to research how to get around, and how to stay respectful to the area. 

I know you‚Äôre coming for one day, but please remember, 

When you leave trash and poop bags on the trails- someone has to pick it up. 

This is not just a permanent home to many locals who have been here for years, but to the wild animals we all share this space with. 

And we are all here because we love nature so much. 

And all we ask of you is that you do your best to leave the least amount of footprint that you can if you do come for a day or two. ‚ù§Ô∏è

This place is magic to us, and we hope you feel the same magic when you‚Äôre here. ü©∑ü¶ãüå≤‚ú®

In fact, it can be called a watch tower to keep a vigil on the Mawal area in the greater province of the Maratha.

description:
Belajar dari Pak dokter @zaidulakbar soal jamu empon-empon yang dicampur air kelapa. Terima kasih dok resepnya.

Menurut Pak Zaidul, manfaat air kelapa + empon2 adalah untuk detox racun dalam tubuh, membersihkan darah, melancarkan menstruasi, dan menjaga kesehatan pencernaan.

Bahan:
- Air kelapa utuh
- 2 jahe ukuran besar
- 4 batang kunyit
- 2 butir temulawak
- Nanas 1/2 buah
- 3 jeruk sunkist
- 1 buah lemon
- Madu secukupnya

Oya guys, ini aku campur nanas dan jeruk sunkist, plus sedikit madu. Rasanya ENAK BANGET. Jadi malah pengen minum terus hahaha. Tp sehari sekali cukup segelas ya, dan jangan lupa air putihnya. Aku minum air putih minimal 10 gelas/hari, atau 2.5 liter/hari. Ini minimal ya, krn akan lebih banyak pas aktivitas padat. 

#jamu #jamutradisional #emponempon #jahe #kunyit #ginger #turmeric #curcuma #healthydrink #healthyfood #healthylifestyle #healthy #health #healthylife #healthyeating

üòçüòç‚Ä¶.. ‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è.. **Celebrating Haryali Teej: A Joyous Festival of Greenery and Devotion üåøüíö**

As the monsoon season blesses the earth with its refreshing showers, we come together to celebrate **Haryali Teej**, a vibrant festival that symbolizes growth, prosperity, and the joy of life. This special day is marked by the lush green surroundings, which signify the name "Haryali" meaning greenery. It's a time for married women to honor their marital bond and pray for the well-being of their husbands, drawing inspiration from the divine love of Lord Shiva and Goddess Parvati.

Women adorn themselves in beautiful green sarees, apply intricate mehndi designs, and sing traditional folk songs. The swings adorned with flowers, the delicious sweets like ghewar, and the exchange of gifts all add to the festive spirit. It's a beautiful celebration of nature, devotion, and togetherness.

Let's cherish the essence of Haryali Teej by embracing the beauty of nature and spreading love and happiness. Wishing everyone a joyous and prosperous Teej! üå∫üéâ
